#: ../../manual/rigging/constraints/transform/copy_location.rst:4
msgid "Copy Location Constraint"
msgstr "Copy Location Constraint 复制位置约束"

#: ../../manual/rigging/constraints/transform/copy_location.rst:6
msgid ""
"The *Copy Location* constraint forces its owner to have the same location as "
"its target."
msgstr "*复制位置* 约束强制约束对象和目标位置相同。"

#: ../../manual/rigging/constraints/transform/copy_location.rst:10
msgid ""
"Note that if you use such a constraint on a *connected* bone, it will have "
"no effect, as it is the parent's tip which controls the position of your "
"owner bone's root."
msgstr ""
"请注意，如果对 *相连* 骨骼使用该约束，将不起作用，因为父级骨骼头部位置决定了"
"该骨骼根部所在位置。"

#: ../../manual/rigging/constraints/transform/copy_location.rst:16
msgid "Options"
msgstr "选项"

#: ../../manual/rigging/constraints/transform/copy_location.rst:20
msgid "Copy Location panel."
msgstr "复制位置面板。"

#: ../../manual/rigging/constraints/transform/copy_location.rst:24
msgid "Target"
msgstr "Target 目标"

#: ../../manual/rigging/constraints/transform/copy_location.rst:24
msgid ""
":ref:`ui-data-id` used to select the constraints target, and is not "
"functional (red state) when it has none."
msgstr ""
":ref:`ui-data-id` 用于选择约束目标，当它为空时此约束不起作用(红色状态)。"

#: ../../manual/rigging/constraints/transform/copy_location.rst:30
msgid "X, Y, Z"
msgstr "X, Y, Z"

#: ../../manual/rigging/constraints/transform/copy_location.rst:27
msgid "These buttons control which axes are constrained."
msgstr "这些复选框用于选择被约束轴向。"

#: ../../manual/rigging/constraints/transform/copy_location.rst:30
msgid "Invert"
msgstr "Invert 反转"

#: ../../manual/rigging/constraints/transform/copy_location.rst:30
msgid "The *Invert* buttons invert their respective preceding coordinates."
msgstr "*反转* 按钮，反转对应轴向的坐标。"

#: ../../manual/rigging/constraints/transform/copy_location.rst:34
msgid "Offset"
msgstr "Offset 偏移量"

#: ../../manual/rigging/constraints/transform/copy_location.rst:33
msgid ""
"When enabled, this control allows the owner to be translated (using its "
"current transform properties), relative to its target's position."
msgstr "启用时，允许约束对象(使用其当前的变换属性)相对于目标位置产生偏移。"

#: ../../manual/rigging/constraints/transform/copy_location.rst:38
msgid "Space"
msgstr "Space 空间"

#: ../../manual/rigging/constraints/transform/copy_location.rst:37
msgid "Standard conversion between spaces."
msgstr "空间之间的标准转换。"

#: ../../manual/rigging/constraints/transform/copy_location.rst:41
msgid "Examples"
msgstr "Examples 示例"

#: ../../manual/rigging/constraints/transform/copy_location.rst:47
msgid "Animation"
msgstr "Animation 动画"

#: ../../manual/rigging/constraints/transform/copy_location.rst:49
msgid ""
"Let us animate the *Copy Location* constraint and its *Offset* button. For "
"example, you can make your owner (let us call it \"moon\") describe perfect "
"circles centered on the (0.0, 0.0, 0.0) point (using e.g. pydriven *LocX*/"
"*LocY* animation curves, see :doc:`Drivers </animation/drivers/index>`), and "
"then make it copy the location of a target (called it \"earth\", for "
"example) with the *Offset* button enabled. Congratulation, you just modeled "
"a satellite in a (simplified) orbit around its planet. Just do the same "
"thing with its planet around its star (which you might call \"sun\", what do "
"you think?), and why not, for the star around its galaxy."
msgstr ""
"让我们来驱动 *复制位置* 约束及其 *偏移量* 。举例说，可以让约束（让我们称之"
"为“月亮”）正好绕圆心点 (0.0, 0.0, 0.0)公转(比如可以用py驱动 *LocX* / *LocY* "
"动画曲线，见 :doc:`驱动 </animation/drivers/index>`)，然后让它复制目标的位置"
"（称之为“地球”）并启用 *Offset(偏移量)* 。恭喜你，你现在模拟出了一颗卫星围绕"
"着行星的运转(简化)。同样的方法可以让行星围绕着恒星(你可能称之为\"太阳\"，你觉"
"得呢？)运转，和为什么不试着让恒星围绕着其星系运转。"

