"件。"

#: ../../manual/rigging/constraints/transform/copy_location.rst:69
msgid ""
"Furthermore you can also animate a few properties of each constraint using "
"animation curves: e.g you can animate the *Influence* of a constraint. It is "
"used to first stick the camera to the \"moon\", then to the \"earth\", and "
"finally to nothing, using two *Copy Location* constraints with *Offset* set."
msgstr ""
"此外，还可以使用动画曲线驱动每个约束的一些属性：例如，可以驱动画约束的 *影响"
"* 。使用两次 *复制位置* 约束和 *Offset* 设置，先使相机跟随“月球”，然后到“地"
"球”，最后回到原位。"
